reviewText: How can I put this in a way so as not to offend or unnerve.  There's a video going all around that you ain't  been getting served.  They say that you ain't you know what and baby VHS are gone.  It's hard to say thank you enough to the people at Amamzon.com!

My favorite Prince video has to be Gett Off. I mean, when I imagine visiting Prince's house, that's pretty much exactly what I picture it's like: music, singing, dancing, fabulous clothes, weird artsy art, gorgeous half-naked chicks all over the place, at any hour of the day or night. Yup, that's what it MUST be like at Prince's house.
